skill.name: Orb of Perception
skill.desc: Fire an orb at the current target that deals magic damage. Launch 3 foxfires at enemies near the target, each dealing true damage. Gain an additional foxfire this combat.

skill.name: Fire Point Strike
skill.desc: Dash to the farthest enemy within 3 hexes, dealing physical damage to them. The next 3 attacks launch kunai at the target, dealing damage.
stats: Total Kunai Damage AD: Kunai AD + Kunai AP

skill.name: Dark Tidings
skill.desc: For the rest of combat, fires an additional arrow at a nearby enemy that deals physical damage. This effect stacks.

skill.name: Traveling Whimsy
skill.desc: Launch a magic missile at the target that bounces 4 times between enemies dealing magic damage to enemies hit. They also take 10% more damage for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Honey Barrier
skill.desc: Gain Shield for 6 seconds.

skill.name: Certain Death
skill.desc:
Leap to the largest group of enemies, dealing physical damage to enemies in a 2-hex radius and Stun them for 1.25 seconds. Then, enter a frenzy, gaining Attack Speed, Omnivamp, and causing attacks to deal bonus physical damage to the target and adjacent enemies.

If already frenzied, empower the next attack to chomp, dealing physical damage.

skill.name: Temporal Anomaly
skill.desc:
Passive: On target death, hookshot to the lowest percent health enemy within 3 hexes and deal physical damage. After a hookshot or Ability cast, the next attack deals true damage.

Active: Knock back and Stun enemies adjacent to the target for 1 seconds, dealing physical damage. Create a containment zone around the target for 4 seconds. Gain 30% Durability and 225% Attack Damage while in the zone.

skill.name: Witch Fang
skill.desc: Empower the next 3 attacks to deal magic damage.

skill.name: Snowfall
skill.desc:
Dash within 2 hexes to hit the most enemies possible and heal. Excess healing becomes a 3 second Shield. Then, deal magic damage to adjacent enemies and magic damage to enemies 2 hexes away.

Every 2 casts create a snowfall that Chills all enemies and heals all allies over 3 seconds. Excess healing also becomes a 3 second Shield.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 20%

skill.name: Training Dummy
skill.desc: Use on a champion to spawn a movable target dummy nearby. Cannot be used in combat.

skill.name: Eldritch Maelstrom
skill.desc:
Passive: Enemies within 2 hexes will run 1 hex away for 1.5 seconds when the Old God enters the battlefield.

Active: Slam the battlefield and Stun all enemies for 6 seconds. Roar to summon 30 lightning strikes that deal magic damage to all enemies randomly over the next 5 seconds.

skill.name: Elder Slam
skill.desc: Deal 240 magic damage to the target and adjacent enemies, Stunning them for 1.25 seconds

skill.name: Earthquake
skill.desc:
Passive: On arrival, Stun all adjacent enemies for 2 seconds.

Active: Deal 150 to the target and all adjacent enemies. For the next 4 seconds, attacks chain lightning 2 times to nearby enemies, dealing 250 magic damage.

skill.name: Sky Spliiter
skill.desc:
Passive: On arrival, Stun all enemies within 2 hexes. Every 3 attacks will chain lightning 4 times to nearby enemies. Lightning deals 85 magic damage.

Active: Deal 375 magic damage to enemies near the target. Then, gain 40% Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Spider Form
skill.desc:
Transform into a spider, replace this Ability with Petrifying Venom, then cast it.

Petrifying Venom: Stun the target for 1.5 seconds and deal magic damage to them. Heal herself.

skill.name: Portalshot Barrage
skill.desc: Fire a blast in a wide line through the current target, dealing physical damage to enemies hit, reduced by 25% for each enemy it passes through. The first target hit takes an additional magic damage. If an enemy is adjacent, blink to safety before firing.

skill.name: Dance of Blades
skill.desc: Leap backward and briefly gain 70% Durability. Then, sweep through the most enemies possible within 2 hexes, dealing physical damage to each one, plus split between all enemies hit.

skill.name: Convergence
skill.desc:
Reduce incoming damage for 4 seconds. Fire two magic bolts that converge on the furthest enemy within 3 hexes, Stunning them. Each bolt deals magic damage to enemies it passes through.

Mage casts will target a different enemy.

skill.name: Snip Snip!
skill.desc:
Dash to a safe position and snip 2 times in a cone. The first and last snip each deal magic damage, while snips inbetween deal magic damage.

Increase the number of snips this combat by 1.

skill.name: Rampage
skill.desc:
Passive: On takedown of the current target, empower the next attack to deal physical damage. If the next target is out of range, charge to them.

Active: For the next 6 seconds, attacks also cleave adjacent enemies for physical damage.

skill.name: Subject: Storm
skill.desc: Paint a lightning bolt on the target. A moment later the bolt strikes, dealing magic damage to the target and magic damage to adjacent enemies. Every 3rd cast, paint 2 extra bolts on the lowest percent Health enemies.

skill.name: Grandmaster-At-Arms
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to adjacent enemies and gain Armor and Magic Resist for 6 seconds. During this time, attacks deal bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Hammer Form
skill.desc:
Transform into hammer form and gain 25 Armor and Magic Resist. Replace this Ability with Hammer Slam and immediately cast it.

Hammer Slam: Leap to the target, dealing physical damage.

skill.name: Get Excited!
skill.desc: Gain 125 decaying Attack Speed for 5 seconds. For the duration, attacks fire rockets that deal physical damage and ignore 50% Armor.

skill.name: Rend
skill.desc:
Passive: Attacks embed a spear in her target. Every 3 / 3 / 1 attacks, also embed spears into nearby enemies.

Active: Deal physical damage to each enemy for each of their embedded spears.

skill.name: Borrowed Time
skill.desc: Attach a temporal rift to the target and the closest unaffected enemy that deals magic damage over 6 / 6 / 4 seconds. Reset the duration of all other rifts on the enemy. If they die while affected, the rift explodes into stardust and heals adjacent allies for 8% of their max Health.

skill.name: Nether Blade
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to the target and gain Shield for 3 seconds. For the rest of combat, attacks deal bonus stacking magic damage.

skill.name: Death Lotus
skill.desc:
Blink to the largest group of enemies within 2 hexes and spin, dealing magic damage over 3 seconds to enemies within 2 hexes and Wounding them for 5 seconds. The 2 nearest enemies take magic damage instead.

If Katarina kills an enemy, she blinks to reposition again.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Hive Ooze
skill.desc: Launches a honey wad through the current target, dealing physical damage to enemies hit. Adjacent allies and allies hit by the trail are set abuzz, gaining Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Dream Bloom
skill.desc: Heal herself, then deal magic damage to the current target.

skill.name: Knick-Knack Attack
skill.desc:
Throw completed items to allies with open slots. If an ally has no room for items, they instead gain a stacking 12% Damage Amp for the rest of combat. Then, throw knick-knacks at enemies that each deal magic damage.

Occasionally, also finds something special in the backpack.

skill.name: Cyclone
skill.desc:
Combat Start: Gain 45 Armor and Magic Resistance. Lose 1 of each every second.

Active: Spin, gaining Shield for 4 seconds and dealing physical damage to each adjacent enemy.

skill.name: Obliterate
skill.desc: Gain Shield that decays over 2 seconds and slam the target, dealing magic damage in a 2-hex line. Gain 12% Damage Amp for the rest of combat.

skill.name: My Lovely Pets
skill.desc: Gain shield for 4 seconds and summon a swarm of bats. They seek out the 4 closest enemies within 3 hexes and deal magic damage each. Bats deal true damage to enemies below 25% Health.

skill.name: Leviathan
skill.desc: Fire a bubble that deals magic damage at the largest group of enemies within range. Every 3rd cast, summon The Leviathan instead, which Stuns and deals magic damage to enemies in a line.

skill.name: Hellhound
skill.desc: Steal Health split between the nearest enemies. Each cast after heals Health and deals physical damage to the target instead.

skill.name: Surprise!!!
skill.desc: Transform into a Crab for 2 seconds. Over the duration, regain 12% + 200 health and release scuttleblasts at 3 nearby allies and 3 nearby enemies. Allies hit are healed; enemies hit take magic damage and are Stunned for 1.25 seconds.

skill.name: Formless Blade
skill.desc:
Passive: Shields grant 60% Attack Speed for 3 seconds.

Active: Dash up to 2 hexes away, then deal physical damage to enemies in a line through the target. Gain Shield for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Fiery Sneeze
skill.desc:
Sneeze fire at the target, dealing physical damage. 50% of overkill damage is dealt to the closest 2 targets.

Dragon Upgrade: Overkill hits 4 targets.

skill.name: Portalpalooza
skill.desc: Launch a ball at the current target that explodes magic damage, and colors the area for 5 / 5 / 15 seconds, dealing magic damage over the duration. If the ball lands in an area that is already colored, it will bounce to a new location within 2-hexes before exploding.

skill.name: Sticky Bite
skill.desc:
Bite the target, healing himself, dealing magic damage, and Chilling them for 3 seconds.

Chill: Reduce Attack Speed by 20%

skill.name: Ragnarok
skill.desc:
Passive: Every 4 attacks and when changing targets, leap at the target and deal physical damage to the target and adjacent enemies.

Active: For the next 5 seconds, gain Attack Speed, Omnivamp, and crowd control immunity.

skill.name: Clean-Up Duty
skill.desc: Gain Shield for 3 seconds. Then, wallop the target dealing physical damage.

skill.name: Gleaming Quill
skill.desc: Gain Shield for 3 seconds and shoot 8 feathers in a wide cone, dealing magic damage to enemies they hit. Then land, granting allies within 2 hexes a Shield for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Molten Caramel
skill.desc:
For 3 seconds, gain Durability and create a cone of flame that deals magic damage over the duration and Wounds enemies for 5 seconds.

Wound: Reduce healing received by 33%

skill.name: Runic Portal
skill.desc: Open portals that fire magic bolts split among the 3 / 3 / 6 closest enemies. Each bolt deals magic damage.

skill.name: Sentinel Smash
skill.desc: Slam the target dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Sharp Note
skill.desc: Fires a soundwave towards the longest line of enemies that deals magic damage, reduced by 35% for each enemy hit.

skill.name: Deathbringer Strike
skill.desc: Deal physical Damage and heal for Health.

skill.name: Heroic Swing
skill.desc:
Passive: Akshan's attacks reduce the target's Armor by 50%.

Active: Akshan launches his grappling hook and swings untargetably toward the farthest enemy, gaining Attack Speed for 4 seconds. Akshan will continue to attack the nearest enemy at double his Attack Speed while swinging.

skill.name: Dark Vigil
skill.desc: Aphelios launches number of attacks, one at the target and the rest at the enemies, dealing physical damage to each.

skill.name: Enchanted Arrow
skill.desc: Ashe fires an arrow at the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage to the first enemy hit and stunning them. If the arrow travels at least 5 hexes, the stun duration is doubled. Enemies within 1 hex receive 50% of these effects.

skill.name: Sear
skill.desc: Launch a ball of fire at the nearest non-seared enemy, searing them for magic damage over 12 seconds. Seared enemies are Shredded.

skill.name: Moonfall
skill.desc: Diana calls forth moonlight, drawing in all nearby enemies, dealing magic damage and stunning them.

skill.name: Spinning Axes
skill.desc:
Passive: Draven ignores 50% his target's Armor.

Draven starts spinning an axe, empowering his next attack to deal bonus physical damage. It will return to his original location after striking the target. If Draven catches it, he will empower the axe again.

Draven can spin up to 2 axes at a time.
stats: Damage: Percent of Attack Damage + Bonus Damage

skill.name: Crowstorm
skill.desc: After a brief channel, Fiddlesticks teleports behind his target and summons a murder of crows for 5 seconds, dealing magic damage per second to all enemies within. Enemies that die within the flock extend its duration by 1 second and heal Fiddlesticks for 25% of their maximum Health.

skill.name: Shield of Durand
skill.desc: Galio charges the area around him for 2.5 seconds, taunting all enemies within while gaining damage reduction. Upon releasing the charge, Galio deals magic damage to all enemies within 3 hexes and heals for % of the damage blocked.

skill.name: God-Lion's Justice
skill.desc:
Garen calls down a sword that strikes a large area around his target, dealing magic damage and reducing their Magic Resist by 50% for 8 seconds.

Garen gains a shield for 5 seconds.

skill.name: Drunken Rage
skill.desc: Gragas drinks from his cask, granting him damage reduction for 4 seconds, and causing his next attack to deal bonus magic damage.

skill.name: Skip 'N Slash
skill.desc: Gwen dashes around her target and performs 3 rapid scissor snips in a cone in front of her, each dealing magic damage. Snips steal Armor and Magic resist from their target. Gwen will perform double the snips in every other cast.

skill.name: Spirit of Dread
skill.desc: Hecarim creates an aura around himself. Each enemy within the aura takes magic damage and heals Hecarim over the duration.

skill.name: Upgrade!!!
skill.desc:
Heimerdinger empowers his Baby Dragon's next attack. The Baby Dragon's overcharged attack launches 3 fireballs across the battlefield, dealing magic damage and burning enemies for 18% of their maximum Health as true damage over 6 seconds, reducing healing by 50% for the duration.

If Heimerdinger does not have a Baby Dragon, this Ability will create one instead.

skill.name: Defiant Dance
skill.desc: Irelia surrounds herself with blades for 4 seconds and gains damage reduction, increasing by 10% each time she attacks, up to 80%. When the effect ends she strikes her target as magic damage.

skill.name: Daisy!
skill.desc:
Ivern summons his sentinel friend Daisy to fight with him. Daisy receives 100% of Ivern's Ability Power and immediately casts Shockwave upon arrival.

If Daisy is already in battle, Ivern increases her Ability Power and commands her to cast Shockwave again.

skill.name: Empowered Strike
skill.desc: Jax slams his target and gains stacking Attack Speed for the remainder of combat. Jax leaps to the nearest enemy if no target is in his Attack Range.

skill.name: Pierce
skill.desc: Kalista hurls a spear towards the farthest enemy, dealing physical damage to the first enemy it hits. If it kills an enemy, the spear continues and will deal any excess damage to the next enemy it hits.

skill.name: Soulflare
skill.desc:
Karma fires a burst of energy towards a random enemy's location that detonates upon impact, dealing magic damage to adjacent enemies, and reducing Karma's maximum Mana (down to a minimum of 10).

Karma empowers every third cast, causing it to launch 3 bursts of energy toward different targets instead of 1.

skill.name: Divine Ascent
skill.desc:
Passive: Kayle ascends every N seconds. Each bonus stacks with the one before, until she is fully ascended.
1st: Attacks deal bonus true damage.
2nd: Attacks explode around the target dealing her Attack Damage and bonus true damage to adjacent enemies.
3rd: Every 12th attack grants Kayle immunity to damage for 1 second.
4th: Attacks cause swords to rain down around the target, dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Flame Rush
skill.desc: Kennen engulfs himself in flame, dashing behind his target, then to the farthest enemy. Enemies he passes through are zapped dealing magic damage and stunning them.

skill.name: Taste their Fear
skill.desc: Kha'Zix slashes the nearest enemy, dealing magic damage. If the enemy has no adjacent allies, this damage is increased.

skill.name: Violent Tendencies
skill.desc:
Passive: Kled deals 200% of his Attack Damage every 4th attack.

Kled enters combat on Skaarl, granting himself a shield. When the shield is broken Kled dismounts, becoming untargetable briefly, gaining Attack Speed.

skill.name: Cripple
skill.desc: Lee Sin slams the ground, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies and slowing their Attack Speed by 50% for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Solar Barrier
skill.desc: Leona creates a barrier around herself, reducing all incoming damage for 4 seconds.

skill.name: The Culling
skill.desc: Lucian faces the farthest enemy and fires shots in that direction for 4 seconds, dashing on occasion to keep hitting enemies. Each shot hits deals physical damage and magic damage. Lucian also fires extra shots based on his Attack Speed.

skill.name: Whimsy
skill.desc: Lulu enchants the units nearest to her. Enchanted allies gain bonus Attack Speed for 5 seconds. Enchanted enemies are stunned and transformed into a docile feline for 1.5 seconds, taking 20% increased damage. If there are less than 3 units nearby, Lulu will enchant herself.

skill.name: Prismatic Illumination
skill.desc: Lux launches her wand toward her farthest ally, then calls the wand back to her hand. The wand shields each ally in its path by for 3 seconds. Lux also empowers her next attack to deal an additional magic damage.

skill.name: Make it Rain
skill.desc: Miss Fortune rains 4 waves of bullets down around her target, dealing magic damage to enemies in the area and reducing their incoming healing by 50% for 6 seconds.

skill.name: Anchor Slam
skill.desc: Nautilus causes the ground beneath his target to erupt, knocking them up, stunning them, and dealing magic damage. Enemies adjacent to the target receive 50% of this effect.

skill.name: Aspect of the Cougar
skill.desc:
Nidalee transforms into a cougar and leaps behind the lowest Health enemy.

While in cougar form, Nidalee gains Dodge Chance, Attack Speed, and her attacks become melee attacks that deal bonus magic damage every 4th attack.

skill.name: Umbra Blades
skill.desc: Passive: Every third attack, Nocturne slashes all adjacent enemies and heals himself for 100% of the damage dealt. If only one target is hit, Nocturne also increases his Attack Speed by 35% for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Consume
skill.desc: Willump bites his target, dealing magic damage. If Willump's target has less Health than he does before the bite, it deals an additional 50% damage and becomes true damage.

skill.name: Berserker Rage
skill.desc: Passive: Olaf gains Attack Speed for each 1% of missing Health, and his attacks heal him.

skill.name: Buckler Toss
skill.desc: Poppy throws her buckler at the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage. The buckler then bounces back, granting Poppy a shield that blocks damage.

skill.name: Phantom Undertow
skill.desc: Pyke leaves a phantom at his location, then dashes behind the farthest enemy. After 1 second, the phantom returns to Pyke, dealingmagic damage and stunning all enemies it passes through.

skill.name: Gleaming Quill
skill.desc: Rakan launches a feather toward his target, dealing magic damage to the first enemy hit. Rakan then heals all nearby allies for % of their missing health, with an increased radius if the feather killed an enemy.

skill.name: Attract and Repel
skill.desc: Rell leaps into the air and creates a tether between herself and her farthest ally. When she lands, the tether breaks, stunning all nearby enemies in its path. This effect also grants a Health shield for 4 seconds to nearby allies in the same area.

skill.name: Blade of the Dawn
skill.desc: Riven empowers her blade, stunning nearby enemies for 1.5 seconds and dealing them magic damage. For the next 8 seconds, she gains bonus Attack Damage.

skill.name: Fury of the North
skill.desc: Sejuani signals Bristle to charge, dealing magic damage and stunning her target. She then gains Frost Armor, granting her Armor and Magic Resist for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Last Embrace
skill.desc: Senna launches black mist toward the farthest enemy. The first enemy hit along the path is stunned, and all nearby enemies are dealt magic damage.

skill.name: Haymaker
skill.desc: After a brief wind up, Sett punches forward in a cone, shredding flat Armor for 10 seconds (stacks) and dealing physical damage to all enemies in the area.

skill.name: Equinox
skill.desc: Soraka calms the area around the enemy with the highest current percent Mana, dealing magic damage to all enemies hit and increasing the cost of their next Ability by 35%.

skill.name: Force of Will
skill.desc: Syndra grabs the nearest enemy and flings them towards the farthest enemy, dealing magic damage to all nearby enemies upon impact and stunning the thrown target.

skill.name: Teemo's Cruelty
skill.desc: Teemo scatters Infernal Souls around a random enemy. When an enemy nears an Infernal Soul (or after 3 seconds), it explodes dealing magic damage to nearby enemies and reducing their Attack Speed by 50% for 3 seconds.

skill.name: Death Sentence
skill.desc: Thresh hooks his farthest enemy with his chain scythe, dealing magic damage and pulling them toward himself.

skill.name: Rocket Jump
skill.desc: Tristana leaps away from enemies and gains Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

skill.name: Feral Instinct
skill.desc:
Udyr swaps between Turtle and Tiger stance with each cast, gaining the following benefits:
Turtle: Gain a Health shield for 4 seconds.
Tiger: Strikes 3 times quickly with his next attack as physical damage.

skill.name: Holy Arrows
skill.desc: Fires a hail of arrows two-hex radius around the current target, Enemies take physical damage. Varus and allies within the radius deal bonus magic damage on attack for the next 6 seconds.

skill.name: Silver Bolts
skill.desc: Passive: Vayne's third attack on a target deals bonus true damage on-hit.

skill.name: Lifeform Disintegration Ray
skill.desc: Vel'Koz channels a ray of energy for 3 seconds toward the enemy nearest the center of the battlefield, dealing magic damage over the duration. The beam widens as Vel'Koz channels, and he will pivot if there are no enemies in the area.

skill.name: Sovereign's Domination
skill.desc:
Viego corrupts the soul of his target for 5 seconds, stunning them and dealing magic damage, increasing 50% each second. Viego will be interrupted if he is stunned, and Viego's allies prefer not to target his victim during soul corruption.

If his victim dies, they are resurrected at full Health to fight for him, but they lose health per second. Resurrected enemies receive the Trait bonuses of Viego's team instead of their own.

skill.name: Transfusion
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to the current target and Heal Health.

skill.name: Doombringer
skill.desc: Volibear leaps toward his target, then slams the ground in a large area around him. This effect knocks up and stuns enemies, dealing magic damage. This damage is doubled against shielded targets.

skill.name: Burning Blade
skill.desc: Yasuo strikes his target, dealing magic damage. He then empowers his blade, gaining stacking bonus true damage on-hit for the rest of combat.

skill.name: Arcane Bomb
skill.desc: Ziggs throws an arcane bomb at his target, dealing magic damage.

skill.name: Grasping Roots
skill.desc: Zyra sends a surge of vines toward her farthest enemy, dealing magic damage and stunning all enemies they hit.

skill.name: Twilight Eruption
skill.desc: Gain Durability for 3 seconds. Create 3 volcanic ruptures under the closest enemies which Stun for 1.5 seconds and deal magic damage. Subsequent ruptures on the same enemy are 50% effective.

skill.name: Dragon's Descent
skill.desc:
Transform into dragon form and gain an aura that deals magic damage per second to adjacent enemies. Then fly through the largest group of enemies within 2 hexes and Stun them.

Dragon Upgrade: Double the size of the aura. It deals 30% more damage.

skill.name: Learning to Fly
skill.desc:
Passive: Fly around and attack the nearest enemy.

Active: Gain Attack Speed and replace Smolder's attacks with fireballs that deal physical damage for 6 seconds.

Dragon Upgrade: Each fireball also heals 20 Health.

Active: Gain Attack Speed and replace Smolder's attacks launch fireballs that deal physical damage.

Dragon Upgrade: Next 6 attacks instead. Fireballs deal physical damage.

skill.name: Starfall
skill.desc: Call down a star on the target that deals magic damage to adjacent enemies then heals a nearby ally.

skill.name: Blizzard
skill.desc:
Transform, gaining max Health. While transformed, deal magic damage to enemies within 2 hexes every second.

If already transformed, gain additional max Health and increase the damage.

skill.name: Transcendence
skill.desc:
Conjure a rift on the target that deals magic damage and 20% Shreds for 6 seconds. This ability upgrades the more it is cast.

15 Casts: Enemies adjacent to the target are Shredded and take magic damage.
30+ Casts: For every 30 casts, create an additional rift on a nearby enemy that deals 30% damage.

Shred: Reduce Magic Resist

skill.name: Divination Dive
skill.desc: Dive underground and surface next to the closest enemy. Send out a shockwave towards the farthest enemy within 4 hexes. Enemies within 2 hexes or hit by the shockwave take magic damage and are Stunned.

skill.name: All Eyes on Me
skill.desc: Gain Durability for 4 seconds and attract nearby enemy projectiles. At the end, release a nova that deals magic damage in a 2 / 2 / 3 hex range.

skill.name: Primordial Breath
skill.desc: Passive: Attacks splash in a cone behind the target.

skill.name: Explosive Charge
skill.desc: Fire a cannonball at the target, dealing physical damage to the first enemy hit. That enemy is knocked back 2 hexes and Stunned if they are within 2 hexes of Tristana.

skill.name: Ice Shard
skill.desc:
Fire a piercing shard of ice that Sunders for 5 seconds and deals physical damage, reduced by 10% for each enemy hit.

Sunder: Reduce Armor

skill.name: Hail of Hellfire
skill.desc: Fire a supernova at a cluster of enemies within Attack Range + 1 hexes that deals physical damage to the target and all adjacent enemies. It explodes into a cluster of fireballs, dealing initial damage as physical damage to all other enemies within three hexes.

skill.name: King Bee's Judgement
skill.desc:
Passive: Gain 2 Ability Power for every Charm you buy.

Active: Deal magic damage to the target.

skill.name: Personal Space
skill.desc: Gain Shield for 4 seconds, increased by 5% for each enemy targeting Vex. When it expires, deal magic damage to enemies within 2 hexes.

skill.name: Voidborn
skill.desc: The Voidspawn gains bonus Health and Attack Damage based on the current Stage.

skill.name: Ravenous Hunter
skill.desc: Passive: Permantly gain 1% Attack Speed and movement speed for each champion killed. Attacks heal for Health and deal bonus physical damage. Gain double the healing and physical damage for targets below 25% Health.

skill.name: Soldier's Sacrifice
skill.desc: On death deal 600-800 magic damage (based on current Stage) to enemies within 1 hexes.

skill.name: WitchFrog
skill.desc: TBA

skill.name: Eye of the Magus
skill.desc: Launch 10 arcane blasts randomly split between the closest 5 enemies that each deal magic damage.

skill.name: Friends Forever!
skill.desc: Every 4 seconds, heal the attached ally for Health and grant them either 10 Ability Power or 10% Attack Damage based on their role, doubled if she heals them over full Health. She grants Ability Power to champions with a "Magic" role and Attack Damage to champions with an "Attack" role.

skill.name: Bouncing Bee
skill.desc: Throw a bouncing bomb at the farthest enemy. The bomb explodes on the first enemy hit dealing magic damage to the target and area damage to all nearby enemies.

skill.name: Time Bomb
skill.desc: Place a bomb on the target, dealing magic damage and Stunning them for 1.25 seconds. When the stun ends or the target dies, the bomb explodes, dealing magic damage to the target and dealing secondary explosion magic damage to adjacent enemies.

skill.name: Trouble Bottle
skill.desc: Deal magic damage to the target and reduce their Magic Resist for the rest of combat.

traits.name: Arcana
traits.desc:
Use the Arcana signifier item to choose a High Arcana champion. Each Arcana grants power based on a different condition.

Gain power for:
Ahri: Fielding 3-star champions.
Hecarim: Equipping items.
Tahm Kench: Activating traits.
Xerath: Purchasing Charms.
Emblem: Equipping Spatula items.

stats.1: Ascendant Charms can appear in your shop. The odds increase by 8% after player combat, up to 40%. When you buy one, the odds reset.

traits.name: Bastion
traits.desc:
Your team gains 10 Armor and Magic Resist.

Bastions gain more, and the value doubles in the first 10 seconds of combat.

stats.8: 140 AR/MR and 2 champions starting combat in the back 2 rows are invulnerable until 4 Bastions die

stats.1: When Morgana's bats kill an enemy, they have a 40% chance abduct a 1-star copy of it.

traits.name: Blaster
traits.desc: Blasters gain Damage Amp, which increases for 3 seconds after casting their Ability.

traits.name: Chrono
traits.desc:
Chronos gain 15 Ability Power.

Combat start: begin a 14 second countdown, which speeds up by 1 second after each Chrono Ability cast. At the end of the countdown, gain a special effect.

stats.2: Your team restores 20% health; Chronos gain 20 Ability Power
stats.4: AND freeze time for 3 seconds, Chronos keep fighting and gain 45 Ability Power
stats.6: Freeze time for 4 seconds, your team heals 100% health; Chronos keep fighting and gain 70 Ability Power and 35% Attack Speed

stats.2: Dragon attacks and Abilities 1% Burn and Wound enemies for 5 seconds.
stats.3: The power of friendship upgrades all dragon Abilities!

stats.1: Wukong does not have a trait bonus, but instead has a powerful Ability and increased stats.

traits.name: Eldritch
traits.desc: When your team loses 20% of their Health, an Old God awakens. It gains 25% Health and 12% Ability Power for each Eldritch star level.

The anvil offers 4 choices.

augments.name: Item Collector I
augments.desc: Your team gains 10 Health. For each unique item they are holding, your team gains bonus 2 Health, 1 Attack Damage, and 1 Ability Power.

augments.name: Item Collector II
augments.desc: Your team gains 20 Health. For each unique item they are holding, your team gains bonus 5 Health, 1.5 Attack Damage, and 1.5 Ability Power.

augments.name: Item Grab Bag I
augments.desc: Gain 1 random completed item.

augments.name: Item Ladder
augments.desc: Gain a temporary item that unequips and transforms at the start of each round. The item quality increases each Stage.

augments.name: Keepers I
augments.desc: Combat start: grant units with adjacent allies a 145 Health Shield for 8 seconds. This Shield stacks.

augments.name: Keepers II
augments.desc: Combat start: grant units with adjacent allies a 230 Health Shield for 8 seconds. This Shield stacks.

augments.name: Lategame Specialist
augments.desc: When you reach Level 9, gain 33 gold.

augments.name: Patient Study
augments.desc: After player combat, gain 2 XP if you won or 3 XP if you lost.

augments.name: Learning To Spell
augments.desc: Your team gains 18 bonus Ability Power, and permanently gains 1 Ability Power every 2 takedowns.

augments.name: Little Buddies
augments.desc: Your 4-cost and 5-cost champions gain 65 Health and 9% Attack Speed for every 1-cost and 2-cost champion on your board.

augments.name: Living Forge
augments.desc:
Gain an Artifact anvil now and after every 8 player combats.

Artifacts are more powerful items with a unique effect.

augments.name: Long Distance Pals
augments.desc: Combat start: Your 2 units furthest from each other form a bond, sharing 22% of their Armor, Magic Resist, Attack Damage, and Ability Power with each other.

augments.name: Latent Forge
augments.desc:
After 8 player combats, gain an Artifact anvil.

The anvil offers 4 choices. Artifacts are more powerful items with a unique effect.

augments.name: Lucky Gloves
augments.desc: Thief's Gloves will always give your champions ideal items. Gain 2 Sparring Gloves.

augments.name: Lucky Gloves+
augments.desc: Thief's Gloves will always give your champions ideal items. Gain 3 Sparring Gloves.

augments.name: Mage Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Mage Emblem and a Galio.

augments.name: Mage Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Mage Emblem, an Ionic Spark, and a Galio.

augments.name: Marksman's Toolbox
augments.desc: Gain a Sniper's Focus. In 3 rounds, gain a Fishbones.

augments.name: Martyr
augments.desc: Whenever one of your allies die, your team heals for 9% of their max Health.

augments.name: Level Up!
augments.desc: When you buy XP, gain an additional 2. Gain 12 immediately.

augments.name: Mentorship I
augments.desc: If an ally starts combat next to a higher-cost ally, it gains 12% Attack Speed and 150 Health.

augments.name: Mentorship II
augments.desc: If an ally starts combat next to a higher-cost ally, it gains 18% Attack Speed and 220 Health.

augments.name: Missed Connections
augments.desc: Gain a copy of each 1-cost champion.

augments.name: Molten Caramel
augments.desc: Gain a Rumble. Your strongest Rumble's Ability deals 190% damage and costs 30 less Mana but no longer reduces damage. Rumble also gains 20% Omnivamp.

augments.name: Molten Caramel+
augments.desc: Gain 2 Rumbles. Your strongest Rumble's Ability deals 190% damage and costs 30 less Mana but no longer reduces damage. Rumble also gains 20% Omnivamp.

augments.name: Multistriker Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Multistriker Emblem and a Kassadin.

augments.name: Multistriker Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Multistriker Emblem, a Quicksilver, and a Kassadin.

augments.name: New Recruit
augments.desc: Gain +1 max team size and a Champion Duplicator.

augments.name: Not Today
augments.desc: Gain an Edge of Night. Champions holding this item gain 35% Attack Speed.

augments.name: Magic Wand
augments.desc: Gain a Needlessly Large Rod. Your units gain 18 Ability Power.

augments.name: One, Two, Five!
augments.desc: Gain 1 random component, 2 gold, and 1 random 5-cost champion.

augments.name: Ones Twos Three
augments.desc: Gain 2 1-cost champion, 2 2-cost champions, and 1 3-cost champion.

augments.name: Over Encumbered
augments.desc: For the next stage, you only get 1 bench slot. After, get 3 item components.

augments.name: Pandora's Bench
augments.desc: Gain 2 gold. At the start of every round, champions on the 3 rightmost bench slots transform into random champions of the same cost.

augments.name: Pandora's Items
augments.desc:
Round start: items on your bench are randomized (except Tactician's Crown and Spatula).

Gain 1 random component.

augments.name: Pandora's Items II
augments.desc:
Round start: items on your bench are randomized (excluding Tactician's Crown and Spatula).

Gain 2 random components.

augments.name: Pandora's Items III
augments.desc:
Round start: items on your bench are randomized (excluding Tactician's Crown and Spatula).

Gain 1 random Radiant item.

augments.name: Patience Is a Virtue
augments.desc: If you did not buy a champion last round, gain 2 free rerolls.

augments.name: Phreaky Friday
augments.desc:
Gain an Infinity Force. After 5 player combats, gain another.

Infinity Force: Artifact that offers tons of offensive and defensive stats

augments.name: Phreaky Friday+
augments.desc:
Gain an Infinity Force. After 3 player combats, gain another.

Infinity Force: Artifact that offers tons of offensive and defensive stats

augments.name: Pilfer
augments.desc: Each round, gain a 1-star copy of the first champion you killed last combat.

augments.name: Pillar of Flame
augments.desc: Gain 2 Shens. Your strongest Shen's Ability no longer grants damage reduction, but now summons a large molten pillar that damages enemies in a large line.

augments.name: Placebo
augments.desc: Gain 8 gold. Your team gains 2% Attack Speed.

augments.name: Placebo+
augments.desc: Gain 15 gold. Your team gains 2% Attack Speed.

augments.name: Portable Forge
augments.desc:
Choose 1 of 4 Artifacts.

Artifacts are more powerful items with a unique effect.

augments.name: Portal Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Portal Emblem and a Kassadin.

augments.name: Portal Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Portal Emblem, a Spear of Shojin, and a Kassadin.

augments.name: Precise Planning
augments.desc: When you win or lose combat by 3 or fewer units, gain 3 gold next round.

augments.name: Preserver Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Preserver Emblem and a Zilean.

augments.name: Preserver Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Preserver Emblem, a Nashor's Tooth, and a Bard.

augments.name: Press the Attack
augments.desc: Your Multistriker's attacks apply a stack on their target for 5 seconds. Every 3rd stack deals true damage equal to 4% of the target's max Health. Gain a Kassadin and an Ashe.

augments.name: Prizefighter
augments.desc: Gain 2 item component(s). Every 4 wins gives you an item component.

augments.name: Pumping Up I
augments.desc: Your team gains 8% Attack Speed now. Each round after, they gain 0.5% more.

augments.name: Pumping Up II
augments.desc: Your team gains 10% Attack Speed now. Each round after, they gain 1% more.

augments.name: Pumping Up III
augments.desc: Your team gains 12% Attack Speed now. Each round after, they gain 2% more.

augments.name: Pyro Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Pyro Emblem and an Akali.

augments.name: Pyro Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Pyro emblem, an Infinity Edge, and an Akali.

augments.name: Radiant Refactor
augments.desc:
Gain a Masterwork Upgrade and 1 component anvils.

Masterwork Upgrade upgrades an item to Radiant!

augments.name: Radiant Relics
augments.desc:
Choose 1 of 5 Radiant items. Gain a Magnetic Remover.

Radiant items are very powerful versions of completed items.

augments.name: Raid Boss
augments.desc: Combat start: Your strongest Bastion gains 20% Health. When other Bastions die, they transfer 20% of their Armor and Magic Resist to it. Gain a Poppy and a Nunu.

augments.name: Raining Gold
augments.desc: Gain 8 gold now and 1 gold every round.

augments.name: Raining Gold+
augments.desc: Gain 18 gold now and 1 gold every round.

augments.name: Recombobulator
augments.desc: Champions on your board permanently transform into random champions 1 cost tier higher. Gain 2 Magnetic Removers.

augments.name: Blistering Strikes
augments.desc: Your team's attacks burn their targets for 5% of their max Health over 5 seconds. Attacks also reduce their targets' healing received by 33%.

augments.name: ReinFOURcement
augments.desc: The next 4-cost champion you buy is instantly upgraded to 2-star. Get 12 gold.

augments.name: Replication
augments.desc: Choose 1 of 3 components. For the next 2 rounds, gain a copy of that component.

augments.name: Restart Mission
augments.desc: Sell all champions on your board and bench. Gain 2 random 2-star 3-costs, 3 2-star 2-costs, and a 2-star 1-cost champion.

augments.name: Risky Moves
augments.desc: Your Tactician loses 20 Health, but after 7 player combats, gain 33 gold.

augments.name: Roll The Dice
augments.desc:
Gain a Rascal's Gloves item. This equips 2 random Radiant items every round.

Radiant items are very powerful versions of completed items.

augments.name: Row Rejuvenation I
augments.desc: Your team has 8% Omnivamp, increased by 1% for every champion that starts combat in that same row.

augments.name: Row Rejuvenation II
augments.desc: Your team has 9% Omnivamp, increased by 1.5% for every champion that starts combat in that same row.

augments.name: Royal Guard
augments.desc: Every 3 seconds, all Faeries restore 6% max Health, and the Faerie Queen gains 100% Attack Damage and Ability Power for every other suriving Faerie. Gain a Lillia and a Tristana.

augments.name: Scapegoat
augments.desc: Gain a Training Dummy and 4 gold. If it is the first to die each player combat, gain 1 gold.

augments.name: Scholar Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Scholar Emblem and an Ahri.

augments.name: Scholar Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Scholar Emblem, a Spear of Shojin, and a Bard.

augments.name: School Mascot
augments.desc: The Eldritch summon is holding beneficial items. The summon gains bonus 10% Health and 30 Ability Power. Gain an Elise and a Syndra.

augments.name: Scoreboard Scrapper
augments.desc: Every round, if you're in the bottom 4, your team permanently gains 1.5% Attack Damage and Ability Power. If you're in the top 4, they have 10% more Health.

augments.name: Shapeshifter Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Shapeshifter Emblem and a Shyvana.

augments.name: Shapeshifter Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Shapeshifter Emblem, a Redemption, and a Shyvana.

augments.name: Shields Up
augments.desc: Your Vangards have 30% stronger shields. Vanguards become immune to crowd control for 6 seconds whenever they gain a shield. Gain a Rumble and a Blitzcrank.

augments.name: Shimmerscale Essence
augments.desc:
Gain a Mogul's Mail. In 5 rounds, gain a Gamblers Blade.

These items give gold as well as combat power.

augments.name: Silver Spoon
augments.desc: Gain 10 XP.

augments.name: Silver Veil
augments.desc: Your team gains 5% Attack Speed and is immune to the first crowd control effect in combat.

augments.name: Slammin'
augments.desc: Gain 1 random Component(s). After each player combat, if there are no items on your bench (other than Consumables), gain 2 XP.

augments.name: Slammin'+
augments.desc: Gain 1 random component(s) and 10 XP now. After each player combat, if there are no items on your bench (other than Consumables), gain 2 XP.

augments.name: Sleight of Hand
augments.desc: Gain a Thief's Gloves. Champions holding this item gain 100 Health and 20% Attack Speed.

augments.name: March of Progress
augments.desc: Gain 3 XP now, and bonus XP equal to your level at the start of every player combat round. You can no longer use gold to level up.

augments.name: Spellblades
augments.desc: Whenever one of your champion casts, their next attack deals bonus magic damage equal to 120% of their Ability Power.

augments.name: Spellcaster's Toolbox
augments.desc: Gain a Manazane. In 3 rounds, gain a Zhonya's Paradox.

augments.name: Spider Queen
augments.desc: Gain a 2-star Elise. Your strongest Elise's Ability no longer Stuns, but poisons her target and the 2 closest enemies with 120% damage over 4 seconds.

augments.name: Spin To Win
augments.desc: Gain 2 Wukongs. Your strongest Wukong's Ability scales with Attack Damage instead of resists. After each cast, Wukong gains stacking 30% Attack Damage and 30% Attack Speed.

augments.name: Stars are Born
augments.desc: The first 1-cost and 2-cost champions you buy are instantly upgraded to 2-star. Gain 7 gold.

augments.name: Stationary Support I
augments.desc: After 8 player combats, gain 1 Training Dummy(s) with 1 permanently attached Support item(s).

augments.name: Stimpack
augments.desc: Gain 4 components after you lose 50 player health.

augments.name: Subscription Service
augments.desc: Now, and at the start of each Stage, open a Shop of 4 unique 4-cost champions and gain 6 gold.

augments.name: Sugarcraft Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Sugarcraft emblem and a Rumble.

augments.name: Sugarcraft Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Sugarcraft emblem, a Redemption, and a Rumble.

augments.name: Support Cache
augments.desc: Choose 1 of 4 Support items.

augments.name: Support Golem I
augments.desc: Gain 1 Golem that fights for your team, holding 1 permanently attached Support item(s).

augments.name: Support Golem II
augments.desc: Gain 1 Golem that fights for your team, holding 2 permanently attached Support item(s).

augments.name: Sweet Tooth
augments.desc: Gain a Nunu. Your strongest Nunu gains 100 Health, 200% Damage Amp per 150 Health, and his heal scales with Health. Whenever his Ability kills an enemy, Nunu permanently gains 35 Health.

augments.name: Teaming Up I
augments.desc: Gain 1 random component and 2 random Tier 3 champions.

augments.name: Teaming Up II
augments.desc: Gain 1 random Support item and 2 random 4-cost champions.

augments.name: The Golden Egg
augments.desc: Gain a golden egg that hatches in 11 turns for a huge amount of loot. Winning player combat speeds up the hatch timer by an extra turn.

augments.name: The Golden Remover
augments.desc:
Gain a Golden Remover and component item anvil.

Golden Remover is an Item Remover with infinite uses.

augments.name: Thorn-Plated Armor
augments.desc: Gain a Bramble Vest. Your Bramble Vests deal 5-100% more damage (based on Stage) and heal the holder for 50% of the damage dealt.

augments.name: Three's a Crowd
augments.desc: Your team gains 75 Health for each unique 3-cost champion on your board.

augments.name: Three's Company
augments.desc: Gain 5 random 3-cost champions.

augments.name: Tiniest Titan
augments.desc: Gain 2 player health and 2 gold after every player combat. Your Tactician also moves faster.

augments.name: Tiniest Titan+
augments.desc:
Gain 2 player health and 2 gold after every player combat. Your Tactician also moves faster.

Gain 8 gold now.

augments.name: Tiny, but Deadly
augments.desc: Your team is 50% smaller, but moves and attacks 30% faster.

augments.name: Tiny Titans
augments.desc: Increase your current and max player health by 30.

augments.name: Trade Sector
augments.desc: Gain a free Shop reroll every round. Gain 1 gold.

augments.name: Built Different II
augments.desc: Your units with no Traits active gain 240-530 Health and 45-60% Attack Speed (based on current Stage).

augments.name: Trait Tracker
augments.desc: The first time you activate 7 non-unique traits for 1 combat, gain 6 random emblems.

augments.name: Transfiguration
augments.desc: Gain a random component. For every 3 Charms you purchase this game, gain another component (max +4).

augments.name: Tri Force I
augments.desc: Your Tier 3 champions gain 150 Health, 10 starting Mana, and 10% Attack Speed.

augments.name: Two Healthy
augments.desc: Your team gains 80 Health for each unique 2-cost champion on your board.

augments.name: Two Tanky
augments.desc: When you field exactly 2 copies of a champion, they both gain 550 Health. When one copy dies, the other gains a 40% max health Shield for 6 seconds. When you 3-star, gain a 2-star copy.

augments.name: Unleash the Beast
augments.desc: Gain a Sterak's Gage. When its effect triggers, the holder gains 45% Attack Speed for the rest of combat and immunity to crowd control for 10 seconds.

augments.name: Upward Mobility
augments.desc: Buying XP costs 1 less. Gain 3 Health and 2 free rerolls whenever you level up.

augments.name: Vanguard Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Vanguard Emblem and a Rumble.

augments.name: Vanguard Crown
augments.desc: Gain a Vanguard Emblem, a Protector's Vow, and a Rumble.

augments.name: Vertically Inclined
augments.desc:
Your team deals 9% more damage.

Deal 18% more damage instead if you have less active non-unique traits than your opponent.

augments.name: Wandering Trainer II
augments.desc: Gain 6 gold and a Training Dummy with 3 permanently attached Emblems.

augments.name: Wandering Trainer I
augments.desc: Gain 1 gold and a Training Dummy with 2 permanently attached Emblems.

augments.name: Warrior Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Warrior Emblem and an Akali.

augments.name: What Doesn't Kill You
augments.desc: Gain 2 gold after losing a player combat. Gain a random component after every 4 losses.

augments.name: What the Forge
augments.desc: Completed items you own (except Tactician's Crown and Emblems) are transformed into random Artifacts. Champions gain 110 Health per equipped Artifact. Gain 1 Artifact Anvil.

augments.name: Witchcraft Crest
augments.desc: Gain a Witchcraft emblem and a Cassiopeia.

augments.name: Witchy Wallops
augments.desc: Gain a 2-star Poppy. Your strongest Poppy's Ability no longer Shields, but strikes 3 times, dealing 80% of the original damage.

augments.name: Worth the Wait
augments.desc: Gain a random 1-cost champion. After 1 rounds, gain another copy of them at the start of each round for the rest of the game.

augments.name: Worth the Wait II
augments.desc: Gain a random 2-cost champion. Gain another copy at the start of each round for the next 8 rounds.

augments.name: You Have My Bow
augments.desc: Gain a Recurve Bow. Your units gain 12% Attack Speed.

augments.name: You Have My Sword
augments.desc: Gain a B.F. Sword. Your units gain 15% Attack Damage.

augments.name: Young and Wild and Free
augments.desc: You can always move freely on Carousel rounds. Gain 2 gold.

augments.name: Zap Attack
augments.desc: Gain a 2-star Blitzcrank. Your strongest Blitzcrank becomes supercharged, dealing magic damage to 2 nearby enemies every 5 seconds and on every Ability cast.
